2843
02:03:37,030 --> 02:03:38,610
Jordan?

2844
02:03:38,610 --> 02:03:41,280
Chúa ơi!

2845
02:03:41,280 --> 02:03:42,870
Anh đã uống gì?

2846
02:03:42,870 --> 02:03:44,240
Anh bị gì thế?

2847
02:03:44,240 --> 02:03:45,330
Jor!

2848
02:03:45,330 --> 02:03:47,790
