2868
02:04:40,470 --> 02:04:41,910
Brad!

2869
02:04:43,510 --> 02:04:45,080
Brad!

2870
02:04:45,470 --> 02:04:46,760
Brad!

2871
02:04:46,770 --> 02:04:49,290
Thằng khốn!

2872
02:04:53,520 --> 02:04:55,480
Mày đã làm gì?

2873
